<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">School of Medicine (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ATA 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ataturk&apos;s Principles and History of Revolution II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">27.03.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Independence War, founding of the Turkish Grand National Assembly, international treaties, peace process, establishment of the Republic, Ataturk’s principles and revolutions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429050&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">School of Medicine (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">TUR 102</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Turkish Language II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">27.03.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes the types of written and oral expression the scientific research and citation process and topics to be considered in oral presentations.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429051&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">School of Medicine (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">EMED 001</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Medical Engineering</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21+28+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students are expected to perform literature surveys, consult experts in understanding the pathophysiology of the disease, origins of the clinical problem and the state-of-art of technology in treating or diagnosing this problem
Students are expected to work in teams in creating their solutions and presenting their idea
Students are expected to present their innovative solution as an oral presentation and a written report
Students are expected to work in teams in creating their innovative solutions to a clinical problem. They will be informed about the processes that involve project development
The solutions proposed should abide with ethical standards and medical regulations. Students are expected to be aware of the social and ethical implications of their solutions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429240&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">School of Medicine (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">EMED 008</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Public Speaking</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21+28+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Attendees are expected to study and gain the essential
knowledge about effective speech making.
Attendees are expected to perform successful team work to
Create, perform and evaluate the effective speeches.
Attendees are expected to perform their speeches.
Attendees are expected to develop and perform
their speeches as a team work based project.
Attendees are expected to be aware of their social ethical
responsibilities when developing and performing their speech.</Data></Cell>
