<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">03.04.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Present a case which should include description of symptoms and mental state features,
a etiological factors, medical/legal/family/substance misuse history, differential diagnoses, a plan of management, assessment of prognosis and risk assessment.
Present a recently published research article in the field of Psychiatry improving your knowledge of statistics and methodology in medical research.</Data></Cell>
