<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Understanding the significance and physiologic principles of laboratory tests employed in the assessment of renal function.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429325&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
