<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MED 406</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Surgery</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Anesthesiology and Reanimation • describe basically the administration and the stages of general anesthesia and to list the general anesthetics, • describe the regional anesthesia administration • describe the local anesthesia mechanisms and to list local anesthetics • list the basic and advanced monitoring techniques used for anesthetic and intensive care of patients • analysis of arterial blood gases and acid-base status</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429276&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
