<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MED 406</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Surgery</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Plastic, Reconstructive&amp; Aesthetic Surgery • define the basic approach to burn and frostbite injuries • learn wound healing principles • define the approach to evaluation of craniofacial disorders, cleft lip &amp; palate, • learn the basic breast reconstruction methods • learn the basic approach to hand and lower extremity injuries • learn the basic approach to maxillofacial traumas • learn the treatment of malignant melanoma and nonmelanoma skin tumors</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429276&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
