<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">School of Medicine (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History Of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">More on Hollywood: The Studio System and Exceptional Auteurs (1930-1945)
Genre development
Films: Michael Curtiz, U.S, Casablanca (1942).
Orson Welles, U.S., Citizen Kane (1941).
Alfred Hitchcock, U.S., Rebecca (1940).</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429298&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
