<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History Of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">European Art Cinema: French New Wave/ Eastern Europe and Former Soviet Union
Films: François Truffaut, France, The 400 Blows (1959).
