<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MED 407</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Transition to Clinical Clerkship</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">o Prepare him/herself, the patient and the environment for PE,
o History taking by checklist
